<br>
Our message board is located at: <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub51.ezboard.com/btribulation8537">pub51.ezboard.com/btribulation8537</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
To join us, you must:<br>
<br>
(a) Read and agree to our Guild Charter<br>
<br>
(b) Create a character profile on GuildMagic<br>
<br>
(c) Hunt with a variety of Members and demonstrate (1) proficiency in playing your class and (2) compatibility (on a personal level) with our Members<br>
<br>
(d) Effectively lead a group comprised of Members and at least one Officer on a hunt in an area of your choosing<br>
<br>
(e) Contribute to the success of one Tribulation raid. Our raid schedule can be found on our Guild Events forum or on GuildPortal.<br>
<br>
Upon completion of these requirements, an Officer or Leader (in consultation with the Members) shall invite you into the guild. After receiving a guild invitation, you will be placed on a thirty day probation, during which time your invitation can be revoked if you act in a manner that reflects badly upon the guild. <br>
<br>
We are presently accepting applications for all classes of characters. However, due to the current composition of the guild, we are unable to accept applications from any character unless they meet the following level requirements:<br>
<br>
Class BRD, Level Required 40<br>
Class BST, Level Required 35<br>
Class CLR, Level Required 35<br>
Class DRU, Level Required 40<br>
Class ENC, Level Required 35<br>
Class MAG, Level Required 35<br>
Class MNK, Level Required 35<br>
Class NEC, Level Required 35<br>
Class PAL, Level Required 40<br>
Class RNG, Level Required 40<br>
Class ROG, Level Required 35<br>
Class SHD, Level Required 35<br>
Class SHM, Level Required 40<br>
Class WAR, Level Required 45<br>
Class WIZ, Level Required 35<br>
<br>
This is not to say that characters under these level requirements have nothing to offer Tribulation; rather, the kinds of experiences and groups we are looking for require that all of us be at least the level listed in order to participate effectively. <br>
<br>
If you are interested in joining Tribulation, send any Member, Officer, or Leader a tell and let them know that you are interested in joining the guild and would like to hunt.<br>
<br>
